Configuration
-------------

User configuration and scan history are stored in:
  ~/.sentinel/

Test Lab
--------

For safe testing, use the included Docker Compose lab:

  cd /usr/share/doc/sentinel/examples/
  docker-compose up -d

This provides:
- OWASP Juice Shop: http://localhost:3000
- WebGoat: http://localhost:8080/WebGoat
- DVWA: http://localhost:8081

Ethical Use
-----------

IMPORTANT: Sentinel is designed for authorized security testing only.

- Use only on systems you own or have explicit permission to test
- Always obtain and document consent before scanning
- Respect rate limits and robots.txt
- Report findings responsibly
- Never use for unauthorized access or malicious purposes

